_:Nf909dbee337f40aca25f36877f339a20 <http://schema.org/name> "Rachel Hanger" .
<https://www.gov.uk/> <http://schema.org/name> "Home" .
_:Nf909dbee337f40aca25f36877f339a20 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Rachel Hanger is a Partner and UK Head of Investment Management &amp; Funds Tax at KPMG London. Rachel advises traditional, hedge fund managers and pension funds on corporate/partnership, product and operational tax issues. Prior to joining KPMG Rachel was Head of Tax at M&amp;G for over 10 years. She was responsible for providing pro-active tax advice to all parts of M&amp;G’s business particularly focusing on product development, risk and operational tax matters.</p>\n\n<p>Rachel has more than 20 years experience in the fund management industry. Prior to joining M&amp;G in 1998, she spent 10 years with another ‘Big 4’ firm including a 2 year secondment to the USA. Rachel is a member of the Institute of Chartered Accountants in England and Wales.</p>\n" .
